    "shareUrn": "urn:li:share:7008061161350799362",
    "text": "💡 As the end of the year is approaching, one starts to wonder what are the things he/she achieved that made a difference this year. What I am particularly proud of are our mock interviews we did for developers from junior communities to help them improve their interviewing skills and get their dream jobs. 👨‍💻👩‍💻\n\nThank you again Ataccama (and especially Barbora Valencikova) for the huge support! Thank you, my great helpers Karolína Filipová (Šelmátová), Anastazija Galac, Matej Grečo  (for intro recruiter rounds) and Adam Drda, Tomáš Belada, Tomáš Pustelník, Pavel Peroutka, Cong Nguyen, Adam Juraszek, Dominik Moštěk, Lukas Polak, Michal Baumgartner, Zdeněk Obst, Bořek Vavřík and others (for tech rounds). \n\nI would also like to thank Honza Javorek (Junior Guru) and Petra Kotuliakova (AjTyvIT) and all other people who shared and reshared my posts about mock interviews again and again to give this chance to as many people as possible. 🙏\n\nWhen I saw the feedbacks from our „candidates“, I realized how happy it made me, and I wanted to share it with you as well. If any one of them is reading this post, I would like to thank to you too for coming and giving us feedback on our interviewing skills as well. 🙂 ❤️\n#mockinterviews",
